text: Matthea Elisabeth Larsen Daughtry (born March 9, 1987) is an American politician. She has been the President of the Maine Senate since 2024. She is a Democrat. She has been a member of the Maine Senate since 2020. She is the youngest Senate president in Maine history. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Maine Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:State legislators of the United States
